    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Acrobolbus mashpianus. A. Part of shoot, dorsal view. B. Part of shoot, ventral view. C. Underleaf, in situ. D. Cells from center of ventral leaf lobe with oil bodies. E. Cells from center of ventral leaf lobe, leaf surface papillae indicated. F. Detail of Plagiochila- type branch, ventral view. G.-J. Leaves. K. Stem cross-section. All drawn from MB 11033 (QCNE)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7517607/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

